Hotfix Notes November / 20 / 2007 
<br />
GENERAL
<br />
Beginning on November 20th, at 5:00 AM PST, Adventurers and Crafters alike will receive a 50% bonus for experience! The bonus XP will kick in as soon as the servers come up from their weekly maintenance at approximately 7:00 AM PST and will remain in effect until next Tuesday's restart.
<br />

<br />
Enjoy the xp bonus and have a wonderful weekend filled with family, friends, food and fun – both in and out of Telon!
<br />

